column5: I stopped by the lake to have my cup of Timmies,While parked,I noticed the pay station was covered up. HMMMM  So I took a drive around and sure enough,they are all covered up. Looks like there will be no charge for parking for the winter anglers.      I will be emailing both townships and ask if they will be doing the same thing.
no, they will not do the same innisfilltheirpocketswithyourmoney will still charge
I'm not sure about that. They were installing those new protection poles this week and this might just be a temporary thing. I guess we'll see.
Rob every where I went,they were covered up. ALL LOCATIONS
the ice looks a bit sketchy, though!!
No plans to plow the lots either....
Covered up due to snow removal..  Found this on the City of Barrie website.  I doubt those parking meters are going anywhere.
